<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
		<title>Topic 4: Broken brute-force protection, IP block</title>
		<script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
		<script
			src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.7.1.min.js"
			integrity="sha256-/JqT3SQfawRcv/BIHPThkBvs0OEvtFFmqPF/lYI/Cxo="
			crossorigin="anonymous"
		></script>
		<style>
			body {
				background-color: #09090b; /* Zinc-950 */
			}
		</style>
		<script>
			$(window).on('load', () => {
				$('#logout-button').on('click', () => {
					fetch('/api/logout', {
						method: 'POST',
						credentials: 'include',
					}).then(() => {
						location.reload();
					});
				});
			});
		</script>
	</head>
	<body class="flex items-center justify-center min-h-screen px-4 text-zinc-100">
		<div class="max-w-xl text-center space-y-6">
			<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-zinc-100">
				Topic 4: Broken brute-force protection, IP block
			</h1>
			<p class="text-zinc-300 text-lg">
				Build and conduct penetration testing on an application that is vulnerable due to a
				logic flaw in its password brute-force protection.
			</p>
			<a
				href="<%= user ? '/profile' : '/login' %>"
				class="inline-block px-6 py-3 bg-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-600 rounded-lg text-white font-medium transition-colors"
			>
				<% if(user){ %>
				Go to
				<%= user.username %>'s Profile →
				<% } else{ %>
				Go to Login Page →
				<% } %>
			</a>
			<% if(user){ %>
			<button
				id="logout-button"
				class="inline-block px-6 py-3 bg-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-600 rounded-lg text-white font-medium transition-colors"
			>
				Logout
			</button>
			<% } %>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>
